# VisionTrackAI

VisionTrackAI is an AI-powered real-time object detection and tracking system built using computer vision and machine learning technologies.

## Features
- Real-time object detection
- Motion tracking
- AI-based image analysis
- Scalable architecture
- Security and automation applications

## Technologies Used
- Python
- OpenCV
- TensorFlow / PyTorch

## Purpose
To provide intelligent visual monitoring solutions for automation, healthcare, surveillance, and smart systems.